Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your favorite bowling alley. My name is Alex. How can I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I'm having some issues with a billing charge on my recent visit.

I'm sorry to hear that. Let's get this sorted out. May I know your name, please?

Sure, my name is Jordan.

Thank you, Jordan. Can I have the date of your visit and the receipt number? It will help me locate the billing details.

I was there on September fourteenth, and the receipt number is three two nine zero.

Got it. Please hang on for a moment while I look up this information.

No problem, take your time.

Thank you for waiting, Jordan. I found the details, and it seems there was a double charge. I'll arrange for a refund of the extra amount right away.

I appreciate that, thank you!

You're welcome, Jordan. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

No, that was it.

Alright, thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a great day!
